@dishId = <pega_el_id_del_plato>

### ─────────────────────────────
### WEEK MENUS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear menú semanal (ADMIN) — week_start_date debe ser lunes
POST {{baseUrl}}/week-menus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "week_start_date": "2026-06-15"
}

###

### Listar todos los menús semanales
GET {{baseUrl}}/week-menus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener menú semanal por ID (incluye items con platos)
GET {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/one?weekMenuId={{weekMenuId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Consultar el menú del día (platos configurados para esa fecha)
GET {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/menu?date=2026-06-16
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─────────────────────────────
### WEEK MENU ITEMS (días del menú)
### ─────────────────────────────

### Agregar línea al menú semanal (ADMIN)
### Requiere ID del tipo de menú y del plato
POST {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/b4989ac5-9e44-4550-ab30-15b873703678/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menu_date": "2026-06-16",
  "menu_type_id": "7ce56068-fe01-4f49-a37c-fdef40531ef8",
  "dish_id": "e5a5d556-f71b-4e34-8485-4192f04ac9dd"
}

###

### Actualizar item del menú (cambiar plato, ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/{{weekMenuId}}/items/{{weekMenuItemId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "dish_id": "{{dishId}}"
}

###

### Eliminar item del menú (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/{{weekMenuId}}/items/{{weekMenuItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
